node.text:
It was a tremendous amount of work I put in to get to 250+ then unload a lot of that weight back down to 189LB. I just wanted to show you guys if you have your mind made up on a goal you can go take what’s yours. When you stop everything else and focus on what you want, you gain what you want by making what’s important a top priority. 

Link in my bio for customized diet and training plans.
